Workflow Plugin for CakePHP 2.x
===============================

1. put in plugins folder. watch for the lowercase of directory name.
    # git submodule add -f git@github.com:egi/workflow.git plugins/workflow

2. load the plugin manually by using this single call in app/Config/bootstrap.php
    CakePlugin::load('workflow'); //Loads a single plugin

3. DB initialization: (from your app directory)
    ./Console/cake schema create --plugin workflow
